           if        rf-oft-cod-arc       not  = rr-cod-fnt
                     go to exe-ass-orf-buf-200.
       exe-ass-orf-buf-420.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se ordine inevaso                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
