           move      2                    to   rf-ofr-dec-vpp         .
           move      "/"                  to   rf-ofr-tdc-vpp         .
           move      001936,27000         to   rf-ofr-cdc-vpp         .
       exe-ass-ofr-lit-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
