                     go to exe-ass-ofr-lit-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Prezzo di riferimento (quello netto)        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-ofr-prz-net       to   rf-ofr-prz-vpl         .
       exe-ass-ofr-lit-600.
       exe-ass-ofr-lit-700.
       exe-ass-ofr-lit-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importi                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Importo definitivo per la riga              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           multiply  rf-ofr-qta-fda       by   rf-ofr-prz-net
                                        giving rf-ofr-imp-rig         .
      *
           if        rf-ofr-dec-prz       =    1
                     divide 10            into rf-ofr-imp-rig
